----------------------------------------------------------------------
WHY THIS LICENSE EXISTS — a plain-English summary, NOT a license term
----------------------------------------------------------------------

Mneme is many years of work compressed into one product. The maintainer
wants you to be able to USE it freely on your own machine, on your own
code, for your own work — that part is genuinely free. What the
maintainer is protecting against is somebody downloading Mneme, changing
the name on the wordmark, slapping their own logo on it, and reselling
it as a competing product. That's the line.

If you want to do something this license doesn't cover and you think it
should, just ask. omanishay@gmail.com.

